    {
      "id": "6a001c6c0000000000e8796e",
      "text": "[https://raw.githubusercontent.com/twitter/twemoji/ad3d3d669bb3697946577247ebb15818f09c6c91/assets/svg/1f34e.svg]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1778392173,
      "updated": 1778392174
    },
    {
      "id": "6a001c2b0000000000e8796d",
      "text": "[赤いりんご.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1778392108,
      "updated": 1778392130
    },
    {
      "id": "6a001b690000000000e87969",
      "text": "[フレデリック・テイラー]と[Frederick Taylor]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1778391913,
      "updated": 1778391931
    },
    {
      "id": "6a001b7b0000000000e8796a",
      "text": "自分はこんな風に日本語版と英語版のページを分けている",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1778391932,
      "updated": 1778391993
    },
    {
      "id": "6a001b8b0000000000e8796b",
      "text": "これは、日本語と英語を混ぜて書くのが自分には負荷が高すぎたため",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1778391948,
      "updated": 1778392083
    },
    {
      "id": "6a001de20000000000e8796f",
      "text": "もちろん、これが唯一の正解だとは思っていない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1778392546,
      "updated": 1778392581
    },
    {
      "id": "6a001bd20000000000e8796c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1778392019,
      "updated": 1778392019
    },
    {
      "id": "69fff47800000000007132fb",
      "text": "#2026-05-10",
